  <fr:p>We deduce that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {isSurjective}\,\left \lvert f\right \rvert _{0}]]></fr:tex> is equivalent to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {isSurjective}\,f]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p>

  

  
