  <fr:p>Incidentally, the appeal to <fr:link
type="local"
href="hottbook.xml"
addr="hottbook"
title="Homotopy Type Theory: univalent foundations of mathematics">Theorem 7.3.12 of the HoTT Book</fr:link> can be replaced by the more general <fr:link
type="local"
